  "text": "Because of the presence of a great number of items the individual counting of which was difficult, it was decided not to analyze the numerical frequency of the items concerned. Thus, in the present study, the percentage frequency of occurrence (FO%) and percentage biomass abundance (M%) [CITATION_1] for each prey item and prey group were calculated.",
